About Me
Hi, I’m Shoon Lae Kyi Myint 👩‍💻
A Technical Project Manager at Moneris and an incoming UBC Master of Data Science student.
I’m passionate about data, product management, and bringing Burmese culture to life through food, storytelling, and tech.
